column5: *combo of pairwise covers with S-R/BCR/Tin or S-R with BCR/Tin
*Combo of S-R and BCR (split on b1,b10 then quad the deg-8 term with 2-aux) we have 3 runs of 2-aux and 1 run of 0-aux
*Combo of S-R with BCR/Tin (split on b5,b6), we have 3 runs with 0-aux and 1 run with 3-aux
